NAME
     implode() - concatenate strings

SYNOPSIS
     string implode( mixed *arr, string del )

DESCRIPTION
     Concatenate all strings  found  in  array  `arr',  with  the
     string  `del'  between  each  element. Only strings are used
     from the array.

